      "author": "laofahai",
      "description": "## What's New\n\n### Smart Column Filtering\n- **Multi-select dropdown**: columns with fewer than 12 unique values now show a checkbox dropdown for multi-value filtering\n- **Date range picker**: date columns get a date picker for min/max range filtering\n- **Number range filter**: number columns support min/max range input\n\n### Auto Encoding Detection\n- Automatically detects GBK, GB2312, Windows-1252, Shift-JIS encoded CSV files\n- Falls back to UTF-8 on detection failure\n- Detected encoding shown in toolbar\n\n### Column Type Detection\n- Auto-detects STRING, NUMBER, DATE types per column\n- Type badge displayed in column header\n\n### Other Improvements\n- Column management: hide/show, drag & drop reorder, freeze columns\n- Persistent column config (widths, order, visibility, freeze state) saved per file\n- Updated README with new features and screenshot",
